separator.name: Separator-Role
separator.recommended:
The Separator Role, it will be applied to Members if they fulfill following conditions:
**Self-Adapting `True`**: 
Looking at the Role list of the Server, The Separator Role will be applied if a Member gains any Role between the Seaprator and the Stop Role, if no Stop Role is defined it stops at the top of the Role List. Any Role moved between these 2 Roles or above the Separator Role will instantly start triggering the Separator Role

**Self-Adapting `False`**:
The Separator Role will be assinged to Members with at least one of the defined Roles
